data.description: This charming single-story home is located on a corner lot in the desirable northwest neighborhood of San Antonio. Boasting three bedrooms, this residence offers a comfortable and functional layout for everyday living. The open floor plan creates a seamless flow between the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it great for entertaining guests or enjoying a cozy evening in front of the fireplace on a winter's night. The property also features an enclosed covered area in the back, providing an ideal spot to enjoy fresh air and savor your morning coffee. With its convenient location, this home offers easy access to nearby amenities, schools, and shopping centers. Don't miss the opportunity to make this delightful home yours and experience the relaxed and inviting lifestyle it has to offer in northwest San Antonio.
